      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine with only minor surface scratches consistent with careful use, while the interior is clean, smoke-free, and shows minimal wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs smoothly, shifts well, and all electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. It serves as a reliable daily driver that requires no immediate repairs, offering a great balance of performance and longevity for its next owner.",
